# Optional. Leave everything commented to use your Claude Code CLI session
# (after `claude login`). Uncomment + fill in if you want to use an API key
# instead. Do NOT leave a placeholder value uncommented — it'll be loaded as
# a real key and cause 401s.
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-paste-your-real-key
# CLAUDE_MAX_TOKENS=2048
# PORT=5050

# CLAUDE_MODEL is now also editable from Settings → AI backend → Model in
# the UI. The DB setting wins over this env var; this is here as a fallback
# for headless / scripted setups. Leave commented to use the built-in
# default (claude-sonnet-4-5) or whatever the UI saved.
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5
